OL,3,CNumber of sudden deaths at Welsh
OL,4,Cprison 'drug related,' says ombudsman
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, March 20, a spokesperson
OL,7,Ffor the Prisons and Probation
OL,8,FOmbudsman initially said they were
OL,9,Funable to make any assumptions as to
OL,10,Fwhether the deaths were at all linked.
OL,12,FHowever, a statement released today
OL,13,F(March 21) by Ombudsman Adrian Usher
OL,14,Fsaid "after initial enquiries, we now
OL,15,Fbelieve at least four out of the six
OL,16,Fdeaths are drug-related.
OL,18,FThe six deaths are among a total of 20
OL,19,Fdeaths at the prison the body has been
OL,20,Fnotified of, and begun investigating,
OL,21,Fsince January 2022.
