OL,4,Cprison 'drug related,' says ombudsman
OL,6,FIn an 'urgent public plea' Mr Usher
OL,7,Fsaid: "Over the last few days, we
OL,8,Fconfirmed that six deaths have
OL,9,Foccurred at HMP Parc in just under one
OL,10,Fmonth. I am saddened by this high
OL,11,Fnumber, and I offer my deepest
OL,12,Fcondolences to those affected."
OL,14,FOmbudsman Adrian Usher added: "These
OL,15,Fdeaths likely involve spice (a
OL,16,Fpsychoactive substance), mixed with
OL,17,Fanother family of drugs."
