OL,3,CNumber of sudden deaths at Welsh
OL,4,Cprison 'drug related,' says ombudsman
OL,6,FA national public health warning has
OL,7,Falready been issued about the afore
OL,8,Fmentioned drug, the name of which is
OL,9,Fyet to be determined.
OL,11,FThe initial enquiries have led prison
OL,12,Fofficials to believe "at least two of
OL,13,Fthe deceased at HMP Parc had taken
OL,14,Fthis substance" with the Ombudsman
OL,15,Fsaying: "It is therefore likely the
OL,16,Fdeaths are all spice-related."
OL,18,FIn his plea, Mr Usher urged all
OL,19,Fprisoners in possession of spice to
OL,20,Fdispose of it immediately.
