OL,4,Cprison 'drug related,' says ombudsman
OL,6,FHe said: "This is a dangerous drug and
OL,7,Fwe do not want to see any more
OL,8,Funnecessary deaths occur. Friends,
OL,9,Ffamily, next of kin, and staff in
OL,10,Fprison ` please share this message as
OL,11,Fwide and as quickly as possible".
OL,13,FThe prison is run by private security
OL,14,Ffirm G4S and is one of the largest
OL,15,Fprisons in the UK, housing more than
OL,16,F1,700 inmates.
