OL,6,FA South Wales Central coroner's
OL,7,Fservice spokesperson said: "As with
OL,8,Fall deaths in custody, an inquest is
OL,9,Frequired and will be opened in the
OL,10,Fusual manner in open court in
OL,11,Faccordance with the Coroner's and
OL,12,FJustice Act 2009. The name and date of
OL,13,Fbirth of the deceased and
OL,14,Fcircumstances of death will be read
OL,15,Finto the public record during the
OL,16,Fopening of the inquest."
